Milky Way shifted♪

115
00:07:02,440 --> 00:07:05,140
♪Still, I never stayed with you♪

116
00:07:05,160 --> 00:07:09,100
♪Through the dark,
seeing a world so bright♪

117
00:07:12,280 --> 00:07:13,130
Don't come any closer!

118
00:07:13,130 --> 00:07:14,210
Xia Mo, this is a trap!

119
00:07:14,210 --> 00:07:15,090
Xia Mo!

120
00:07:16,250 --> 00:07:17,170
Professor Mu.

121
00:07:17,930 --> 00:07:19,850
She really cares about you.

122
00:07:30,090 --> 00:07:32,130
I told you to stay away from my sister.

123
00:07:34,090 --> 00:07:35,290
Now she's hurt because of you.

124
00:07:36,210 --> 00:07:37,090
Mo.

125
00:07:38,370 --> 00:07:39,290
Xinyi.

126
00:07:39,810 --> 00:07:41,410
He didn't hurt me.

127
00:07:41,690 --> 00:07:43,010
It was the J Organization.

128
00:07:45,370 --> 00:07:46,290
Why are you still here?

129
00:07:46,690 --> 00:07:47,690
Your presence

130
00:07:47,690 --> 00:07:49,410
will only bring her more trouble.

131
00:07:50,090 --> 00:07:51,130
Leave.

132
00:07:55,210 --> 00:07:56,250
You're hurt too.

133
00:07:57,090 --> 00:07:58,610
You should go home and rest.

134
00:07:59,500 --> 00:08:00,600
I'm fine, really.

135
00:08:02,570 --> 00:08:03,450
Leave.

136
00:08:39,050 --> 00:08:40,770
I told you not to mess with my sister.

137
00:08:42,610 --> 00:08:44,290
She came to me on her own.

138
00:08:44,810 --> 00:08:46,090
I was just defending myself.

139
00:08:46,930 --> 00:08:47,930
Doesn't matter.

140
00:08:49,490 --> 00:08:52,090
Anyone who hurts my sister pays.

141
00:09:00,570 --> 00:09:01,930
Dying by your hand

142
00:09:02,610 --> 00:09:03,490
is worth it.

143
00:09:07,490 --> 00:09:08,610
I love you.

144
00:09:19,050 --> 00:09:19,930
Love...

145
00:09:25,250 --> 00:09:27,090
If hurting me eases your anger,

146
00:09:28,170 --> 00:09:29,290
I'm willing.

147
00:09:31,250 --> 00:09:32,130
Love?

148
00:09:32,570 --> 00:09:34,090
Stop pretending.

149
00:09:34,570 --> 00:09:35,690
I won't end you today

150
00:09:35,690 --> 00:09:37,530
because you once saved me.

151
00:09:37,890 --> 00:09:40,050
But if you touch my sister again,

152
00:09:40,730 --> 00:09:42,490
I'll make sure you pay.

153
00:09:57,370 --> 00:09:59,490
Did you forget Operation Witch Hunt?

154
00:10:00,810 --> 00:10:02,650
That was our promise.

155
00:10:03,330 --> 00:10:04,770
From now on,

156
00:10:05,610 --> 00:10:06,730
we go our separate ways.

157
00:10:09,570 --> 00:10:10,610
There is no "us".

158
00:10:30,690 --> 00:10:31,570
Dad,

159
00:10:32,250 --> 00:10:33,130
Mom,

160
00:10:34,130 --> 00:10:36,210
thank you for protecting me

161
00:10:37,370 --> 00:10:38,610
and changing the contract,

162
00:10:41,140 --> 00:10:42,260
and that's what saved me.

163
00:10:47,370 --> 00:10:49,370
But Xia Mo lost her necklace

164
00:10:49,930 --> 00:10:51,290
and suffered for five years.

165
00:10:53,130 --> 00:10:54,850
I owe her so much more.

166
00:10:55,730 --> 00:10:56,930
What am I supposed to do now?

167
00:10:58,330 --> 00:10:59,210
Dad,

168
00:10:59,730 --> 00:11:01,050
can you tell me

169
00:11:02,370 --> 00:11:03,570
what should I do?

170
00:11:20,930 --> 00:11:24,290
♪On nights when I can't sleep♪

171
00:11:24,610 --> 00:11:28,050
♪Loneliness fills my heart♪

172
00:11:28,690 --> 00:11:31,770
♪Lost in restless thoughts alone♪

173
00:11:35,410 --> 00:11:38,810
♪The moonlight shines down the hall♪

174
00:11:38,810 --> 00:11:40,610
♪Like a land of tender solace♪

175
00:11:42,570 --> 00:11:46,090
♪But I can't catch the light♪

176
00:11:49,930 --> 00:11:53,250
♪When I struggle so hard alone♪

177
00:11:53,650 --> 00:11:57,090
♪Loving with all my heart
leads to letdown♪

178
00:11:57,690 --> 00:12:00,770
♪The grown-up world feels so tense♪

179
00:12:04,570 --> 00:12:07,770
♪Then you show up by my side♪

180
00:12:08,050 --> 00:12:10,090
♪Stay with me through thick and thin♪

181
00:12:10,730 --> 00:12:14,010
♪Your eyes hold a steady gaze♪

182
00:12:14,330 --> 00:12:16,970
♪I keep that look close to my heart♪

183
00:12:17,090 --> 00:12:20,610
♪If you happen to look at the moon too♪

184
00:12:20,930 --> 00:12:24,410
♪Let the moon say what I wish to tell you♪

185
00:12:24,650 --> 00:12:27,970
♪All those simple moments we share♪

186
00:12:27,970 --> 00:12:31,410
♪Are honestly all I ever wish for♪

187
00:12:31,610 --> 00:12:35,050
♪If you happen to look at the moon too♪

188
00:12:35,210 --> 00:12:40,250
♪Please remember how the Milky Way burns♪

189
00:12:41,370 --> 00:12:44,370
♪In this endless sea of people♪

190
00:12:44,490 --> 00:12:48,010
♪You're the one who shines the brightest♪
